item.title: 【Unreleased/Unofficial (lossless)】FLAC - Taylor Swift - Midnights: The Complete Edition | .FLAC 16bits ／ 44.1kHz
item.description:
i put together the acoustic versions of "Lavender Haze" and "Anti-Hero", as well as "You're Losing Me (From The Vault)", "Anti-Hero (feat. Bleachers)" [all these from Qobuz] and the songs from the target version: "You're on Your Own, Kid (Strings Remix)" and "Sweet Nothing (Piano Remix)" [these are from the CD version]. i converted all the songs to 16bit, except for the tracks in the target version, as they came in standard 16bit. in total, 29 songs, enjoy!
